comment: Nice bold flavors, glad I found this in my travels.
There is nothing too much of anything in this whiskey, except at times sweet.  Everything else is just pure smoothness, this is a great everyday single malt whiskey.
$9 and less for HH is great but the flavor profilenis a tweener. Don't ice it next time even a couple cubes like you did. Taste varies from Irish to scotch to bourbon.
Most approachable, spicy and full bodied whiskey I’ve had

Whiskey library. American California whiskey. 
Tastes like building a house with your bare hands feels.
